{
  "id": "2026733767",
  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"piAvSlTB\">在许多老球迷的印象流里，中国乔丹不单只是一个“品牌”，更是对中国男篮名宿胡卫东的尊称。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"5fBgBFLh\">某种意义上，过去只要说起中国乔丹，必然会想起<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=2&amp;q=%E8%83%A1%E5%8D%AB%E4%B8%9C&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">胡卫东<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"erdrI-NJ\">但就这些天下来，我发现中国乔丹，还有一位女性代表得到了绝大多数球迷的公认，她就是中国三人女篮核心-王丽丽。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5d88b6875ff4c806dfd8c221efa3ce59_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"925\" data-rawheight=\"582\" data-original-token=\"v2-c946250647d344288cd7abba72e51faa\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-61e6c2c339085dfa9c27acac5c74ad0b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"925\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5d88b6875ff4c806dfd8c221efa3ce59_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='925' height='582'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"925\" data-rawheight=\"582\" data-original-token=\"v2-c946250647d344288cd7abba72e51faa\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-61e6c2c339085dfa9c27acac5c74ad0b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"925\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5d88b6875ff4c806dfd8c221efa3ce59_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5d88b6875ff4c806dfd8c221efa3ce59_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"m5TE7DUt\">相信大家昨日都已见证了中国代表团<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%90%83&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">三大球<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>项目在本届奥运上获得的首枚奖牌，王丽丽带着杨舒予、张芷婷、万济圆，第一次出征奥运就不负此行，打破了<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%AF%AE%E7%90%83&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">中国篮球<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>史上29年不拿牌的尴尬。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"FX-0MEqv\">现在再回忆一下昨晚面对<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">法国<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>的焦灼，依然是热血沸腾，尤其最后一分钟双方拉锯，真的，拼的就是赢球的信念。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0af67365993d187caf4b2317889b68a2_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"1196\" data-original-token=\"v2-86a5504d16b5aa736f61c48a2c279621\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2dc3b755e7c14ee21a6824aff95a1837_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-0af67365993d187caf4b2317889b68a2_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='960' height='1196'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"1196\" data-original-token=\"v2-86a5504d16b5aa736f61c48a2c279621\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2dc3b755e7c14ee21a6824aff95a1837_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-0af67365993d187caf4b2317889b68a2_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0af67365993d187caf4b2317889b68a2_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"mNe49-uG\">最后25.8秒暂停时，虽然中国还处于领先，但王丽丽单膝跪地，<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=2&amp;q=%E5%BC%A0%E8%8A%B7%E5%A9%B7&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">张芷婷<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>弯腰扶膝，每个人几乎已是累到麻痹，要知道他们在3个小时前面对<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E4%BF%84%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>才累趴过一次。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"Is9t206f\">可作为老大姐，王丽丽还是与队友们相互鼓励着：<b>“掩护就换、别给两分。”“打死不能给两分。”</b></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"reoDZj5C\">也就是这种打死不能给分的信念，中国姑娘成功防下远投、抢下篮板、逼迫对方失误，最终把铜牌抢到了怀里。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2d2616e1895624454dbbb863da54be06_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1056\" data-original-token=\"v2-7aac3be1bdd0ecd527e214e72301d874\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c704ab7163aacd4d4787ce20b4edc363_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2d2616e1895624454dbbb863da54be06_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='1056'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1056\" data-original-token=\"v2-7aac3be1bdd0ecd527e214e72301d874\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c704ab7163aacd4d4787ce20b4edc363_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2d2616e1895624454dbbb863da54be06_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2d2616e1895624454dbbb863da54be06_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"tBidCPdH\">未能率队杀入决赛，的确有些遗憾，但这个铜牌对于整个中国篮球来说，含金量其实不亚于冠军，正如无数人赛后感慨的，中国篮球，竟然也有开光的时候。  </p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"GNAG_0tT\">开光的同时，我们还迎来了自己的女乔丹。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"JHX-AqGT\">如果说颜值爆表的杨舒予是凭借又帅又能打火出了圈，那么王丽丽就是以又飒又能钢的大姐风范彻底征服了众人。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8bebcd540988fd9611751866a1bd64b8_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"900\" data-rawheight=\"500\" data-original-token=\"v2-c92d4a5f36053e14def57fad766a5329\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-27cd0989b93000f9e4e8bbfa0b3584b4_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"900\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-8bebcd540988fd9611751866a1bd64b8_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='900' height='500'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"900\" data-rawheight=\"500\" data-original-token=\"v2-c92d4a5f36053e14def57fad766a5329\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-27cd0989b93000f9e4e8bbfa0b3584b4_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"900\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-8bebcd540988fd9611751866a1bd64b8_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8bebcd540988fd9611751866a1bd64b8_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"fg0Pc5ad\">季军之战足足打了7分45秒，全场11投5中得到9分，全场最高。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"iJuIeWFi\">关键时刻抢下4个篮板，还完成2次突破得分，只有1次失误，可以说没有王丽丽乔丹级别的个人表演就没有三人女篮的历史性突破。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee595955c0d9f6049371a11a3f8877fd_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"251\" data-original-token=\"v2-ee595955c0d9f6049371a11a3f8877fd\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee595955c0d9f6049371a11a3f8877fd_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ee595955c0d9f6049371a11a3f8877fd_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><div class=\"GifPlayer css-1isopsn\" data-size=\"normal\" data-za-detail-view-path-module=\"GifItem\"><img class=\"ztext-gif\" width=\"500\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee595955c0d9f6049371a11a3f8877fd_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee595955c0d9f6049371a11a3f8877fd_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-size=\"normal\" alt=\"动图封面\" style=\"display: block;\"><div class=\"GifPlayer-icon css-d39tw7\"><svg width=\"50\" height=\"50\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><ellipse fill=\"#000\" opacity=\"0.45\" cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"30\" ry=\"30\"></ellipse><ellipse stroke=\"#FFF\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" opacity=\"0.5\" cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"26\" ry=\"26\"></ellipse></g><svg x=\"16\" y=\"18.5\"><g fill=\"#fff\"><path x=\"100\" y=\"100\" d=\"M12.8422852,12.9814453 L12.8422852,11.3994141 L7.63916016,11.3994141 L7.63916016,13.0517578 L10.9086914,13.0517578 L10.9086914,13.3242188 C10.8911133,15.2050781 9.46728516,16.4707031 7.39306641,16.4707031 C5.01123047,16.4707031 3.51708984,14.625 3.51708984,11.6367188 C3.51708984,8.70117188 5.00244141,6.84667969 7.34912109,6.84667969 C9.08056641,6.84667969 10.284668,7.68164062 10.7768555,9.2109375 L12.7543945,9.2109375 C12.3237305,6.64453125 10.2319336,5.00976562 7.34912109,5.00976562 C3.79833984,5.00976562 1.50439453,7.61132812 1.50439453,11.6542969 C1.50439453,15.75 3.77197266,18.3076172 7.36669922,18.3076172 C10.6889648,18.3076172 12.8422852,16.2246094 12.8422852,12.9814453 Z M17.5180664,18 L17.5180664,5.31738281 L15.5493164,5.31738281 L15.5493164,18 L17.5180664,18 Z M22.659668,18 L22.659668,12.7441406 L28.1088867,12.7441406 L28.1088867,11.0039062 L22.659668,11.0039062 L22.659668,7.11035156 L28.6098633,7.11035156 L28.6098633,5.31738281 L20.690918,5.31738281 L20.690918,18 L22.659668,18 Z\"></path></g></svg></svg></div></div></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"sFKW6zEW\">事实上，穿着23号像乔丹，眼神坚定如乔丹，各种单打似乔丹，从奥运三人篮球小组赛开始，<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=7&amp;q=%E7%8E%8B%E4%B8%BD%E4%B8%BD&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">王丽丽<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>就曾以超巨表现冲上过热搜。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"0-2qsX2H\">什么是超巨？就是常规时间稳定，越到关键时刻越不普通。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"8W65a-b6\">奥运9场比赛下来，王丽丽场均出场6.9分钟，交出5.5分4.0篮板的数据，能突能投，能顶能防，除了铜牌争夺战中的神挡杀神，在1/4决赛时，王丽丽同样以11分4篮板超神输出率领<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E9%98%9F&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">中国队<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>挺进半决赛。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4f58f0cd12d9668d3311794c05901dc_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"925\" data-rawheight=\"580\" data-original-token=\"v2-96b524b3b5fca805ae4df364f13ad550\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7a19020a135943ee290fe1e4980153df_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"925\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b4f58f0cd12d9668d3311794c05901dc_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='925' height='580'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"925\" data-rawheight=\"580\" data-original-token=\"v2-96b524b3b5fca805ae4df364f13ad550\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7a19020a135943ee290fe1e4980153df_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"925\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b4f58f0cd12d9668d3311794c05901dc_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4f58f0cd12d9668d3311794c05901dc_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"MFfr-tPe\">拿到铜牌后，王丽丽俯下身子捂住了脸，难掩热泪，围在身边的队友也都擦着眼泪，拍了拍她，彼此之间说不出一句话。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"sWvL20HY\">对于更年轻的张芷婷，万济圆，<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=3&amp;q=%E6%9D%A8%E8%88%92%E4%BA%88&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">杨舒予<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>来说，她们的眼泪可能更多伴随着对未来的期待与憧憬，而对于已快步入三旬的王丽丽而言，这或许是遗憾的开始。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d827acd29c0131287ab4ee4c7a91532_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"359\" data-original-token=\"v2-4d827acd29c0131287ab4ee4c7a91532\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d827acd29c0131287ab4ee4c7a91532_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4d827acd29c0131287ab4ee4c7a91532_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><div class=\"GifPlayer css-1isopsn\" data-size=\"normal\" data-za-detail-view-path-module=\"GifItem\"><img class=\"ztext-gif\" width=\"640\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d827acd29c0131287ab4ee4c7a91532_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d827acd29c0131287ab4ee4c7a91532_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-size=\"normal\" alt=\"动图封面\" style=\"display: block;\"><div class=\"GifPlayer-icon css-d39tw7\"><svg width=\"50\" height=\"50\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><ellipse fill=\"#000\" opacity=\"0.45\" cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"30\" ry=\"30\"></ellipse><ellipse stroke=\"#FFF\" stroke-width=\"2\" 