age zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"502\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-91f91b3372f2447f7b10b97c01fee7e8_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><div class=\"GifPlayer css-1isopsn\" data-size=\"normal\" data-za-detail-view-path-module=\"GifItem\"><img class=\"ztext-gif\" width=\"502\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-91f91b3372f2447f7b10b97c01fee7e8_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-91f91b3372f2447f7b10b97c01fee7e8_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-size=\"normal\" alt=\"动图封面\" style=\"display: block;\"><div class=\"GifPlayer-icon css-d39tw7\"><svg width=\"50\" height=\"50\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><ellipse fill=\"#000\" opacity=\"0.45\" cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"30\" ry=\"30\"></ellipse><ellipse stroke=\"#FFF\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" opacity=\"0.5\" cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"26\" ry=\"26\"></ellipse></g><svg x=\"16\" y=\"18.5\"><g fill=\"#fff\"><path x=\"100\" y=\"100\" d=\"M12.8422852,12.9814453 L12.8422852,11.3994141 L7.63916016,11.3994141 L7.63916016,13.0517578 L10.9086914,13.0517578 L10.9086914,13.3242188 C10.8911133,15.2050781 9.46728516,16.4707031 7.39306641,16.4707031 C5.01123047,16.4707031 3.51708984,14.625 3.51708984,11.6367188 C3.51708984,8.70117188 5.00244141,6.84667969 7.34912109,6.84667969 C9.08056641,6.84667969 10.284668,7.68164062 10.7768555,9.2109375 L12.7543945,9.2109375 C12.3237305,6.64453125 10.2319336,5.00976562 7.34912109,5.00976562 C3.79833984,5.00976562 1.50439453,7.61132812 1.50439453,11.6542969 C1.50439453,15.75 3.77197266,18.3076172 7.36669922,18.3076172 C10.6889648,18.3076172 12.8422852,16.2246094 12.8422852,12.9814453 Z M17.5180664,18 L17.5180664,5.31738281 L15.5493164,5.31738281 L15.5493164,18 L17.5180664,18 Z M22.659668,18 L22.659668,12.7441406 L28.1088867,12.7441406 L28.1088867,11.0039062 L22.659668,11.0039062 L22.659668,7.11035156 L28.6098633,7.11035156 L28.6098633,5.31738281 L20.690918,5.31738281 L20.690918,18 L22.659668,18 Z\"></path></g></svg></svg></div></div></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"HouGNRP3\">说实话，竞技体育方面，女性一向处于劣势，如果不是在某个大赛上成绩出众，估计没有多少人会真正去认识并理解她们。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"wqEVvci0\">就拿王丽丽来说，不知道的还以为她是专门练三人的，其实不然，她曾率领过北大登顶过CUBA，自己也收获过最有价值球员，只是后来初入职业赛场，没多少出场时间的她，一下就淡出了人们的视野。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c17eac178497918fc1eabf696fa66450_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"471\" data-rawheight=\"779\" data-original-token=\"v2-2bd3b3810c2e8bdb45f2af1b749902a6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f27f40256a6833ade42967197fe45cb_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"471\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c17eac178497918fc1eabf696fa66450_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='471' height='779'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"471\" data-rawheight=\"779\" data-original-token=\"v2-2bd3b3810c2e8bdb45f2af1b749902a6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f27f40256a6833ade42967197fe45cb_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"471\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c17eac178497918fc1eabf696fa66450_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c17eac178497918fc1eabf696fa66450_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"CvDL4Q4g\">直到15年加盟新疆女篮，王丽丽才逐渐成长为WCBA的大腿级人物，其实也算是从职业五人篮球临时转场三人篮球。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"L5L_OG6I\">时间和结果都证明了，选择王丽丽出任核心是最为明智的选择，哪怕是打全场，也少有人跟他一样控球、组织、篮板、抢断、三分、突破无所不能。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3c5d3b07e9f1809ef3eb87afd6167ee_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"638\" data-rawheight=\"320\" data-original-token=\"v2-e3c5d3b07e9f1809ef3eb87afd6167ee\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3c5d3b07e9f1809ef3eb87afd6167ee_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"638\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e3c5d3b07e9f1809ef3eb87afd6167ee_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><div class=\"GifPlayer css-1isopsn\" data-size=\"normal\" data-za-detail-view-path-module=\"GifItem\"><img class=\"ztext-gif\" width=\"638\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3c5d3b07e9f1809ef3eb87afd6167ee_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3c5d3b07e9f1809ef3eb87afd6167ee_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-size=\"normal\" alt=\"动图封面\" style=\"display: block;\"><div class=\"GifPlayer-icon css-d39tw7\"><svg width=\"50\" height=\"50\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><ellipse fill=\"#000\" opacity=\"0.45\" cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"30\" ry=\"30\"></ellipse><ellipse stroke=\"#FFF\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" opacity=\"0.5\" cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"26\" ry=\"26\"></ellipse></g><svg x=\"16\" y=\"18.5\"><g fill=\"#fff\"><path x=\"100\" y=\"100\" d=\"M12.8422852,12.9814453 L12.8422852,11.3994141 L7.63916016,11.3994141 L7.63916016,13.0517578 L10.9086914,13.0517578 L10.9086914,13.3242188 C10.8911133,15.2050781 9.46728516,16.4707031 7.39306641,16.4707031 C5.01123047,16.4707031 3.51708984,14.625 3.51708984,11.6367188 C3.51708984,8.70117188 5.00244141,6.84667969 7.34912109,6.84667969 C9.08056641,6.84667969 10.284668,7.68164062 10.7768555,9.2109375 L12.7543945,9.2109375 C12.3237305,6.64453125 10.2319336,5.00976562 7.34912109,5.00976562 C3.79833984,5.00976562 1.50439453,7.61132812 1.50439453,11.6542969 C1.50439453,15.75 3.77197266,18.3076172 7.36669922,18.3076172 C10.6889648,18.3076172 12.8422852,16.2246094 12.8422852,12.9814453 Z M17.5180664,18 L17.5180664,5.31738281 L15.5493164,5.31738281 L15.5493164,18 L17.5180664,18 Z M22.659668,18 L22.659668,12.7441406 L28.1088867,12.7441406 L28.1088867,11.0039062 L22.659668,11.0039062 L22.659668,7.11035156 L28.6098633,7.11035156 L28.6098633,5.31738281 L20.690918,5.31738281 L20.690918,18 L22.659668,18 Z\"></path></g></svg></svg></div></div></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"GRoJZxxn\">当然，王丽丽不是神，她的每一项技能都建立在疯狂的训练基础之上，人家是专项训练，他是全套训练，可想而知这平日训练量有多么的恐怖。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"U_MK4oLK\">在入选三人篮球国家队时，所有教练都评价她是一个特别吃苦的运动员，这足以印证她的天赋并没有大家想象的那么无敌，一切都是汗水的功劳。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b39eea1e7784be209b13b4eb0f2187bd_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"995\" data-rawheight=\"912\" data-original-token=\"v2-75b2c19e578232ebe9d45f0f82bbf670\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8ca2104ee4cd4fc0f1b15bf92ef34794_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"995\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-b39eea1e7784be209b13b4eb0f2187bd_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='995' height='912'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"995\" data-rawheight=\"912\" data-original-token=\"v2-75b2c19e578232ebe9d45f0f82bbf670\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8ca2104ee4cd4fc0f1b15bf92ef34794_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"995\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-b39eea1e7784be209b13b4eb0f2187bd_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b39eea1e7784be209b13b4eb0f2187bd_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"hi86YK-0\">近些年来，不少人都说中国篮球存在多方面的人情世故，但王丽丽却让人觉得是肉眼可见的中流砥柱，就像<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%98%93%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%94&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">易建联<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>之于男篮。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"gCAyvQPT\">事实上，<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=398579859&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=2&amp;q=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%A5%B3%E7%AF%AE&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">中国女篮<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>已经不止一次在世界级的舞台上给过我们惊喜，我也希望日后，当我们谈论起中国乔丹的时候，千万不要忽略了王丽丽的名字。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-dff853f0fa444eeeff49ac21f24fd061_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"680\" data-rawheight=\"620\" data-original-token=\"v2-88f3762358f41a90875612084afb1e38\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8339f2c33d7f1b9fd89a23ef92905028_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"680\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-dff853f0fa444eeeff49ac21f24fd061_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='680' height='620'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"680\" data-rawheight=\"620\" data-original-token=\"v2-88f3762358f41a90875612084afb1e38\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8339f2c33d7f1b9fd89a23ef92905028_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"680\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-dff853f0fa444eeeff49ac21f24fd061_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-dff853f0fa444eeeff49ac21f24fd061_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p><br> </p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
  "excerpt": "在许多老球迷的印象流里，中国乔丹不单只是一个“品牌”，更是对中国男篮名宿胡卫东的尊称。\n\n\n\n\n某种意义上，过去只要说起中国乔丹，必然会想起胡卫东。\n\n\n\n\n但就这些天下来，我发现中国乔丹，还有一位女性代表得到了绝大多数球迷的公认，她就是中国三人女篮核心-王丽丽。\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n相信大家昨日都已见证了中国代表团三大球项目在本届奥运上获得的首枚奖牌，王丽丽带着杨舒予、张芷婷、万济圆，第一次出征奥运就不负此行，打破了中国篮球史上29年不拿牌的尴尬。\n\n\n\n\n现在再回忆一下昨晚面对法国的焦灼，依然是热血沸腾，尤其最后一分钟双方拉锯，真的，拼的就是赢球的信念。\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n最",
